        <div class="card-title">What is Northbeam?</div>
        <div class="prose"><p>Northbeam is an AI-powered marketing attribution platform built for DTC ecommerce brands that spend significant budget across multiple ad channels. It uses machine learning to determine which touchpoints in a customer's journey actually drove a purchase — giving you a more accurate picture of channel performance than Meta, Google or TikTok report independently.</p><p>The core problem Northbeam solves is the same one Triple Whale addresses — ad platforms all take full credit for every sale, making it impossible to know your true ROAS per channel. Northbeam's ML models analyse your first-party data to build a realistic attribution model that reflects how customers actually discover and buy from your brand.</p><p>Northbeam is positioned at the premium end of the attribution market — it's typically used by brands spending $50,000 or more per month on paid advertising where accurate attribution decisions have meaningful financial impact. Its media mix modelling helps brands understand the true incremental impact of each channel.</p></div>
      </div>
