        <div class="card-title">Key Features</div>
        <div class="features-grid"><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🎯</div><div class="feat-name">ML Attribution</div><div class="feat-desc">Machine learning attribution models that go beyond last-click — reflects true customer journey across all touchpoints.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📊</div><div class="feat-name">Media Mix Modelling</div><div class="feat-desc">Understand the true incremental impact of each channel — essential for optimising large ad budgets across platforms.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📈</div><div class="feat-name">Real-Time ROAS</div><div class="feat-desc">Live ROAS tracking per channel, campaign and ad — updated continuously as orders come in.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🔍</div><div class="feat-name">Creative Analytics</div><div class="feat-desc">See which creatives are driving the most efficient revenue — cut losers and scale winners faster.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🛒</div><div class="feat-name">Shopify Integration</div><div class="feat-desc">Deep Shopify integration pulls order and customer data — first-party data foundation for all attribution models.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📋</div><div class="feat-name">Custom Dashboards</div><div class="feat-desc">Build dashboards showing exactly the metrics your team needs — from CMO overview to channel manager detail.</div></div></div>
      </div>
