          <div class="pros"><div class="pc-title">What we love</div><div class="pc-item">Most sophisticated ML attribution available</div><div class="pc-item">Media mix modelling for large budgets</div><div class="pc-item">First-party data foundation — privacy-safe</div><div class="pc-item">Real-time data across all channels</div><div class="pc-item">Strong for brands with complex multi-channel mix</div></div>
          <div class="cons"><div class="pc-title">Watch out for</div><div class="pc-item">Expensive — enterprise pricing</div><div class="pc-item">Requires significant ad spend to get value</div><div class="pc-item">Longer setup and onboarding</div><div class="pc-item">Overkill for brands under $50K/mo ad spend</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Frequently Asked Questions</div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How is Northbeam different from Triple Whale? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Both Northbeam and Triple Whale solve the attribution problem for ecommerce brands, but they target different segments. Triple Whale is more accessible — starting at $129/month and useful for brands spending $5,000+/month on ads. Northbeam is positioned for larger brands spending $50,000+/month and offers more sophisticated media mix modelling. For most growing DTC brands, Triple Whale is the better starting point.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Does Northbeam work with Meta and Google? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Yes — Northbeam integrates with Meta Ads, Google Ads, TikTok, Snapchat, Pinterest and all major ad platforms. It pulls spend and impression data from each platform and combines it with your Shopify revenue data to build a unified attribution model across all channels.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How much does Northbeam cost? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Northbeam does not publicly list pricing — it is sold via custom contracts based on ad spend and data volume. It is a premium product positioned for brands with substantial ad budgets. Contact Northbeam directly for a pricing discussion and demo.</div></div>
